						               													<description>A tabletop about deduction and deception&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A card based game, featuring monsters on a party, playing with voodoo dolls.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player is a voodoo doll trying to discover his opponents identity or defeat'em in the processes, using the monsters weaknesses to attack and block enemies attacks.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is played by rounds. On your turn you draw cards form deck of cards with several objects that you will use to attack your opponents.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You will deal damage to your opponent health points, each player has 3 health points, the player who reches 0 is out.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Every monster has different wekanesses, so that will give you a clue of our opponents identities.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You can use the objects to block your enemies attacks as well, for example holy water blocks fire, and fire blocks holy water (burning its blessing)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You also have some special potions sush as health potions that you can use to heal yourself, or revealing potions to reaveal the blocking cards of your enemies.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You can try to guess your enemies identity, but if you fail the attempt, you lose 2 health points, if you sucess your enemy is out.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
